<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:wght@200..700&family=Nunito:wght@200..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: #51545e;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .order-details {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-details th,
        .order-details td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }
        .order-details th {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .order-details td {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .order-details tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .total {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #6b6e76;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Course Order is Confirmed</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table class="order-details">
                <tr>
                    <th>Order #</th>
                    <th>Item</th>
                    <th>Date</th>
                    <th>Cost</th>
                    <th>Qty</th>
                    <th>Subtotal</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order._id %></td>
                    <td><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td><%= order.date %></td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p class="total">Total Amount: $<%= order.price %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com">michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 HTU LMS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
